    "body": "## Motivation\r\n\r\n1. Enable CUDA graph draft extend support for `trtllm_mla_backend`\r\n2. Fix accept length degradation (~35% drop) when draft extend CUDA graph is enabled with DP Attention\r\n\r\n## Modifications\r\n\r\n1. Add `TRTLLMMLAMultiStepDraftBackend` support in `eagle_worker_v2.py` to enable CUDA graph capture for draft extend\r\n2. Fix `num_tokens_for_logprob_per_batch` / `global_num_tokens_for_logprob_gpu` to match `num_tokens_per_batch` in CUDA graph runners:\r\n   - `eagle_draft_extend_cuda_graph_runner.py`: capture and replay stages\r\n   - `multi_layer_eagle_draft_extend_cuda_graph_runner.py`: replay stage\r\n   - `multi_layer_eagle_worker_v2.py`: draft extend initialization\r\n\r\n**Root Cause**: `num_tokens_for_logprob_per_batch=1` caused `LogitsMetadata.compute_dp_attention_metadata` to calculate incorrect `dp_local_num_tokens`, resulting in MLP sync only processing partial tokens.\r\n\r\n## Accuracy Tests\r\n\r\n**Before (accept_len ~1.5)**:\r\n```\r\n[DP0 TP0] Decode batch, accept len: 1.52, accept rate: 0.51, cuda graph: True\r\n[DP1 TP1] Decode batch, accept len: 1.42, accept rate: 0.47, cuda graph: True\r\n```\r\n\r\n**After (accept_len ~2.3)**:\r\n```\r\n[DP0 TP0] Decode batch, accept len: 2.20, accept rate: 0.73, cuda graph: True\r\n[DP1 TP1] Decode batch, accept len: 2.34, accept rate: 0.78, cuda graph: True\r\n[DP2 TP2] Decode batch, accept len: 2.54, accept rate: 0.85, cuda graph: True\r\n[DP3 TP3] Decode batch, accept len: 2.41, accept rate: 0.80, cuda graph: True\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Config**: TP4 + DP4 + EP4, `speculative-num-steps=2`, `speculative-eagle-topk=1`, `trtllm_mla` backend\r\n\r\n```\r\nexport SGLANG_ENABLE_SPEC_V2=\"1\"\r\npython3 -m sglang.launch_server --model-path /home/hostuser/.cache/huggingface/hub/models--nvidia--DeepSeek-R1-0528-NVFP4-v2/snapshots/25a138f28f49022958b9f2d205f9b7de0cdb6e18 --served-model-name dsr1 --tensor-parallel-size 4 --data-parallel-size 4 --expert-parallel-size 4 --enable-dp-attention --moe-dense-tp-size 1 --attention-backend trtllm_mla --moe-runner-backend flashinfer_trtllm --quantization modelopt_fp4 --kv-cache-dtype fp8_e4m3 --mem-fraction-static 0.8 --chunked-prefill-size 16384 --disable-radix-cache --speculative-algorithm EAGLE --speculative-num-steps 2 --speculative-eagle-topk 1 --speculative-num-draft-tokens 3 --port 30000 --host 127.0.0.1 --watchdog-timeout 1800 --dist-timeout 3600\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\npython -m sglang.test.run_eval --eval-name longbench_v2 --host 127.0.0.1 --port 30000 --model nvidia/DeepSeek-R1-0528-NVFP4-v2 --max-context-length 128000 --max-tokens 16384 --num-threads 16\r\n```\r\n**LongBench V2**: Score = 0.576\r\n\r\n## Benchmarking\r\n\r\n### Kernel:\r\n\r\nBecore:\r\n<img width=\"1201\" height=\"187\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/6ce67bb9-6154-4432-b4eb-7bd9adc19e1f\" />\r\n<img width=\"962\" height=\"292\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a40c01fe-2b53-4b79-a783-ffbe01869ce4\" />\r\nAfter:\r\n<img width=\"933\" height=\"206\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bdf9edc1-e9ab-44c5-ad06-d3c7b045d0ce\" />\r\n<img width=\"786\" height=\"487\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9aec3616-0e18-4b4e-9cfa-8d64f6c4c578\" />\r\n<img width=\"1713\" height=\"337\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/59409c44-0c78-4f87-b9dc-59e7afc626da\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n### E2E (isl: 1024, osl: 1024, bs: 100)\r\nBefore:\r\n```\r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          9231.23\r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        4242.55\r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           21883.00\r\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\r\nMean TPOT (ms):                          15.13\r\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        12.51\r\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           64.41\r\n```\r\nAfter:\r\n```\r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          9415.81\r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        4251.08\r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           21841.32\r\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\r\nMean TPOT (ms):                          12.85\r\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        11.93\r\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           28.39\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Checklist\r\n\r\n- [x] Format your code according to the [Format code with pre-commit](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#format-code-with-pre-commit).\r\n- [ ] Add unit tests according to the [Run and add unit tests](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#run-and-add-unit-tests).\r\n- [ ] Update documentation according to [Write documentations](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#write-documentations).\r\n- [x] Provide accuracy and speed benchmark results according to [Test the accuracy](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#test-the-accuracy) and [Benchmark the speed](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#benchmark-the-speed).\r\n- [x] Follow the SGLang code style [guidance](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#code-style-guidance).",
